snippet.textDisplay:
RIP Slim Shady: 1997 – 2002
Cause of Death: “Poetic” murder
The Culprit: Marshall Mathers
His Weapon: Drug addiction and the fact that everything from “Lose Yourself” onwards has just not sounded like Slim Shady AT ALL (The Eminem Show is where I draw the line – and even that album wasn’t really Slim Shady…an example is “Drips”)
Most Remembered For: The Slim Shady LP, The Marshall Mathers LP, and (I guess) The Eminem Show – three of hip-hop’s alltime best albums
Buried By: Revival, with a hint of “Mom’s Spaghetti” (it’s ready)
Hope y'all enjoyed this obituary lmao!
